nodes.bodyText:
Usually, we tend to use either a ternary:
def previewCommand = isPullRequest() ?
  "jx preview ..."
  : "jx step helm install..."

or the traditional form:
if (isPullRequest()) {
  ...
} else {
  ...
}

It avoids assigning the variable twice and is easier to read.

